Class CollaborationExchangeClient

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.assetmanager.client.ExchangeClientBase
org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.assetmanager.client.CollaborationExchangeClient
All Implemented Interfaces:
CollaborationExchangeInterface
public class CollaborationExchangeClient extends ExchangeClientBase implements CollaborationExchangeInterface
DataElementExchangeClient is the client for managing comments, ratings, likes and tags.
